---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Nutrition', url: '/for-providers/nutrition' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Nutrition Services on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your animal nutrition and diet consultation services on the BreederHQ Marketplace. Be seen by breeders, buyers, and pet owners searching for nutrition guidance in their area."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-emerald-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🥗</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Nutrition Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Diet consultants, raw feeding specialists, and animal nutritionists -
        breeders, buyers, and pet owners in your area are searching for nutrition services on the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-600">
        List Your Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What people search for</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Breeders</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Breeding and lactation diet plans</li>
            <li>Litter weaning protocols and first-food guidance</li>
            <li>Raw feeding formulation for breeding programs</li>
            <li>Performance and conditioning diets for show animals</li>
            <li>Stud dog and breeding male nutrition programs</li>
            <li>Puppy pack diet sheets for new owners</li>
            <li>Bulk feeding plans for multi-animal households</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">From Buyers &amp; Pet Owners</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>New pet diet transition plans</li>
            <li>Food allergy identification and elimination diets</li>
            <li>Weight management programs</li>
            <li>Raw feeding guidance for beginners</li>
            <li>Senior pet nutrition and joint support diets</li>
            <li>Sensitive stomach and digestive health plans</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for nutrition providers</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🔄</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ongoing adjustments</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Diets change with every life stage: pregnancy, lactation, weaning, growth, and aging. One client means years of consultations as their animals' needs evolve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">People search by location and species. Whether someone needs a raw feeding plan or allergy management, they find providers in their area first.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Verification builds trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Upload your credentials for a verified badge. Verified listings get more inquiries because people know you're the real deal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Service profile with consultation types, specialties, and approach</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Coverage area and location-based discovery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Photos and sample meal plans</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Flexible pricing display</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Optional verification badge for credentials</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Breeder recommendations from your clients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 to-emerald-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"><span class="line-through opacity-60 text-2xl">$5/mo</span> Free during early access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-200 mb-3">No commissions. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-200 mb-8">One listing puts your services in front of everyone searching for nutrition guidance on the marketplace.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-emerald-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50">
        List Your Services
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
